title: Refrigerator Toe Kick - Stainless
description: Refrigerator Toe Kick - Stainless PartSelect Number PS1518161 Manufacturer Part Number WR74X10222

installationInstructions.author: Scott from Danville, CA
installationInstructions.title: The toe kick on my refrigerator was damaged during a move.
installationInstructions.content: I removed the 2 screws holding the damaged toe kick and replaced it with the new one.  The repair took less than a minute to do and it's good as new.
